nc2xpJsG_ecO9TFiUPjGdSpJbuO3HFdA&oe=66F3E7A4"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Cover-Art_Landscape.png", "id": "1359054188017007", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75221331_1359054191350340_4019135738094483709_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZQ8oOlx6TgoQ7kNvgEs8SGn&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=ABeeoKjnA-XzLbFeldjkG5u&oh=00_AYADzA6NgjbE253Td_OWbEJCXW98iIwOxYZbn5xabFLfRg&oe=66F3F65B"}, "display_name": "Zoe", "keywords": ["nocode", "collaboration", "learning", "creation", "social"], "long_description": "*new* Apply to become a Zoe content publisher and start building Mixed Reality experiences today!\n\nZoe enables the rapid creation of interactive 3D scenes through a no-code interface and automation. Invite your friends, students, colleagues and clients to collaborate, learn and create together in real-time. \n\nWhat can I create with Zoe?\n\nWith Zoe you can create anything you have in mind. It has been used to host activities, create learning games, build interactive stories, adventure games, and even mini-games for therapy.\n\nOur free version includes templates, creator tools and multiplayer capabilities for up to 3 members. Visit zoeimmersive.com to learn how you can increase the number of collaborators.\n\nReady to use Templates\nEnvironments\n350+ Local Assets\n1M+ Free Online Assets Through Sketchfab\n3 Projects and 3 Scenes Per Project\nUnlimited Interactions\n\n", "short_description": "For ages 13 and up\n\nZoe enables the rapid creation of interactive 3D scenes through a no-code interface and automation. Invite your friends, students, colleagues and clients to collaborate, learn and create together in real-time. \nWhat can I create with Zoe?\nZoe has been used to host immersive workshops, virtual classrooms, project-based-learning activities, meetups, events, interactive art, marketing campaigns, and even mini-games for therapy.\n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_